name: Baby GAN PEPE
description:
From the unconditional love of the Green Android and the mysterious tricks of GANg Pepe to make girls fall in love, this little boy grew up.

It is a strange creature...

Sometimes his father forgets him on the beach and that causes long arguments in this green family. But nothing that a bouquet of Green Roses can't fix.

-


(This creature is given to those who own the Green android & the GANg PEPE)
